# Functional requirements

## Purpose

Capture behaviour the system must provide. Use stable identifiers `REQ-FUNC-NNN` and keep each requirement testable.

## Conventions

- One main behaviour per requirement where possible.
- Include inputs, outputs, preconditions, and notable edge cases.
- Map to user journeys (`REQ-JOR-*`) and acceptance criteria (`REQ-ACE-*`) when relevant.

